author: USA TODAY, Ryan W. Miller, USA TODAY
title: European travelers brought coronavirus to New York long before first case confirmed, studies suggest
description: Scientists studying the coronavirus  genomes found that COVID-19 was spreading in New York as early as January and it didn't come from China.
content:
As the COVID-19 pandemic continues, Americans wonder if the illnesses they had earlier this year were actually a result of the novel coronavirus.
